&nbsp;|&nbsp;
  <a href="/account/delete" class="text-danger">Delete Account</a>
</p>
   <p class="text-light small"><span data-bs-toggle="tooltip" title="This explains what this field does." style="cursor: help; color: #0dcaf0; font-weight: bold;">?</span> Are markers you can hover to get more info on a field
</p>
<p class="text-light small"><span class="text-danger">*</span> are required fields</p>
   
